      "side": 1,
      "message": "After doing some research, I found people suggest to use datastore GetAll instead of goroutines (https://groups.google.com/g/google-appengine-go/c/nAZvStUPkYI). I also compared the runtime for goroutines and  luci datastore.Get in Dev. There is no big difference between them. I saw the underlaying implementation of luci datastore.Get handles those batch Fetches in certain way. So utilizing the existing func is better than writing the goroutines on the client side.",
